{"tid":371390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【天鴿襲澳】最新片段曝光！水淹停車場 多人爬牆逃生","createTime":"2017-08-23T16:14:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-24T07:38:26.000Z","uid":48093,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aa06e65dbdd243ae016a3fb5e2c38fff419c921a","tid":371390,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T16:14:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170823/large/1503501562_c28c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170823%2Flarge%2F1503501562_c28c.jpg&h=29d211f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170823/large/1503501563_e3ab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170823%2Flarge%2F1503501563_e3ab.jpg&h=e1689eb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170823/large/1503501065_6563.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170823%2Flarge%2F1503501065_6563.jpg&h=11f7eb60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【23:50更新】據現場消息稱，停車場內雜物太多，加上裡面又窄又多彎，目前蛙人根本進入停車場內，只能得水泵將水抽走，才可以進行搜救<br />\n<br />\n強颱風「天鴿」直撲澳門，至少釀成當地5死153傷。據澳門民防行動中心代理指揮官、消防局局長梁毓森表示，有3個地方均有人報稱多人被困，分別是沙梨頭典雅灣停車場、灝景峰停車場，以及大興街恆德大廈的停車場，海關及消防局人員由接報起已馬上派出人員在現場搜救，並安排水泵車等工具進行排水，至目前為止未有發現有人員被困。當局正繼續進行搜索和排查，如有進一步消息，將即時對外公佈。據悉，由於全部停車場處於地庫，有傳多人為了救車進入停車場而被困。<br />\n<br />\n網上流傳一段短片，上載者聲稱是灝景峰停車場內的情況，從片段可見，停車場內水浸幾近天花板，大量雜物浮於水面，環境幽暗，一名男子於水中搜救被困人士，旁邊有人用電筒協助照明，水中懷疑有人形物體，有人大聲指揮稱「(個人)喺鐵筒前面，唔好急唔好急，慢啲」，搜救人員即回應「見到見到」。<br />\n<br />\n另外，網上亦流傳多段短片，可見有大量泥水猶如瀑布般湧入灝景峰停車場，水流湍速，猶如瀑布般湧入。而另一段片則懷疑是停車場出口，下面行車路則變成一條急流，數名人士爬上圍牆出口逃生，有人在頂部協助救人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170823/57119398\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170823%2F57119398&d=ecFjVELq14VfTjn935Hzli7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=93e69dd6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170823%2F57119398&h=40f82157\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170823/57119398</a>"},{"pid":"dc06c44da3b2fd0656b7f455ae061ef7a8a124c1","tid":371390,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T17:02:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"553a3fdaf8c2b074b9be8020636d819e61ecc1ac","tid":371390,"uid":82640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T17:02:55.000Z","msg":"RIP"},{"pid":"b3d0ea239d731fb798c223f39c8d8681cfbdc952","tid":371390,"uid":26451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T17:08:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"65f7106d46c9135d98535b77b52529e3b89ddea3","tid":371390,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T17:18:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28f96cd9e241bed4a74574cbafc45763299c89f5","tid":371390,"uid":82640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T17:57:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/24/015730_4cf1de98f2f91fab4e7e6ce603da2a84.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F24%2F015730_4cf1de98f2f91fab4e7e6ce603da2a84.png&h=bc6b405a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"26de74ddc3feac407dc3e49fd265f368052f5e04","tid":371390,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T17:58:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a5926d7692a8f9ebf040bb6e6d0e00a2c2c256e","tid":371390,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor